snippet.title: The Vast White - Teaser
snippet.description:
Add to your wishlist: https://store.steampowered.com/app/3301000/The_Vast_White/

Explore an old mountain at your pace in this openworld snowboarding adventure. Uncover hidden paths, experience dynamic weather, and explore stunning landscapes as you ride. Every path holds new secrets.
